item.title: In the Stars His Handiwork I See
item.description: In the stars His handiwork I see, On the winds He speaks of majesty Though He ruleth over land and sea What is that to me? I will celebrate Nativity, For it has its place in history Sure, He came to set His people free What is that to me? Till one day I met Him face to face And I felt the wonder of His grace, Then I knew that He was more than just a
